OL,3,C'A stain on society': Over 3 million
OL,4,Cfood bank parcels handed out in record
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FA record 3.1 million food bank
OL,8,Femergency parcels have been handed out
OL,9,Fin a single year across the UK.
OL,11,FThe Trussell Trust food bank network
OL,12,Fsaid 3,121,404 parcels were
OL,13,Fdistributed by food banks in its
OL,14,Fnetwork up to the end of March. Just
OL,15,Funder 40% of those were given to
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,18,FThe number of parcels being
OL,19,Fdistributed is now almost double that
OL,20,Fof five years ago.
